    "clinical_pearls": [
      "Young stroke or brain abscess = screen for HHT and pulmonary AVM",
      "All HHT patients need pulmonary AVM screening (contrast echo \u2192 CT if positive)",
      "Antibiotic prophylaxis before dental procedures if pulmonary AVMs present",
      "Do NOT embolize hepatic AVMs - causes biliary necrosis"
    ]
